These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: lettuce, pumpkin, peach, potato, orange, plum, papaya
There are 7 different nationalities: italian, pakistani, indian, british, thai, japanese, polish
 1. the person eating peach is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating potato is not the japanese##6
 3. the italian is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 4. the polish is somewhere to the right of the thai##5
 5. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
 6. the italian is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 7. the person eating plum is somewhere between the person eating pumpkin and the pakistani##7
 8. the pakistani is on the left of the polish##1
 9. the british is somewhere between the person eating orange and the indian##7
10. the indian is on the left or right of the italian##3
11. the thai is on the far left##1
12. the person eating potato is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
13. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person eating plum##5
14. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the right of the person eating orange##5
15. the person eating orange is the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | peach    | lettuce    | pumpkin | plum | potato | orange    | papaya |
| Nationality   | thai | italian | indian  | japanese   | british    | pakistani | polish |

