.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: carrot, apple, peach, garlic, eggplant, cauliflower, avocado
The people have 7 different hobbies: fishing, video-games, woodworking, puzzles, filmmaking, photography, cooking
 1. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere between the person eating avocado and the person eating apple##7
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person eating garlic##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
 5. the person eating carrot is somewhere between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is video-games##7
 6. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere between the person eating garlic and the person who's hobby is woodworking##7
 7. the person eating eggplant is somewhere between the person eating garlic and the person eating apple##7
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person eating eggplant##5
10. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
11. the person who's hobby is photography is not the person eating avocado##6
12. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
13. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person eating garlic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | avocado  | peach | cauliflower | garlic | carrot     | eggplant | apple  |
| Hobby   | woodworking | photography | video-games  | cooking  | filmmaking | puzzles      | fishing |

