 3. the fan of gospel is not the person who's hobby is gardening##6
 4. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the right of the fan of pop##5
 5. the fan of reggae is between the fan of pop and the person who's hobby is camping##2
 6. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the fan of salsa and the fan of indie##7
10. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
11. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is camping is not the fan of reggae##6
13. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is camping##7
14. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
15. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
16. the person who's hobby is camping is not the fan of pop##6
17. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
18. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
19. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the fan of salsa##5

.:: Answer ::.
