12. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
13. the person driving the car is somewhere between the person who's sport is soccer and the person driving the bus##7
14. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person driving the airplane##1
15. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
16. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
17. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
18. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
